<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<div class="body facial">
   <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-6 menu">
      <h1 id="title">Corrective Peels</h1>
      <p>PCA Skin professional products are scientifically formulated to gently stimulate, firm, and tighten skin. PCA Skin treatments are carefully blended to remove dull, damaged surface layers without the downtime often associated with chemical peels. These treatments increase the natural skin cell turnover resulting in healthy, beautiful skin. These superficial peels will result in little to no downtime. Most clients find it unnecessary to apply makeup, as the skin will be smooth, dewy, and radiant following their treatment. Progressive, not aggressive, is the philosophy.
      <br><br>
      <strong>First time getting a PCA peel? All our peels include an initial free skin care consultation, application of the peel, application of customized corrective serums and a post procedure skin care kit. A series of peels is the most effective way to address any skin issue and obtain optimal results. We offer a special price when you purchase a package of 3 and 6 treatments.</strong></p>
    
      <div class="row" id="table-head">
            <div class="col-md-4">Service name</div>
            <div class="col-md-2">Cost</div>
            <div class="col-md-3">Time</div>
            <div class="col-md-3"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- <div class="row" id="table-body"> -->
          
          <% @chemical_peels.order("id asc").each do |service| %>
              <div class="row" id="table-row">
                  <div class="col-md-4" id="table-cell">
                    <%= service.service_name %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-2" id="table-cell">
                    $<%= service.cost %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-3" id="table-cell">
                    <%= service.time %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-3" id="table-cell">
                   <button type="button" class="nav-btn" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modal-<%= service.id %>">Details</button>
                  </div>
              </div>
              
                  <!-- Modal -->
                  <div id="modal-<%= service.id %>" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                    <div class="modal-dialog">

                      <!-- Modal content-->
                      <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <button type="button" class="btn close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                            <h4 class="modal-title"><%= service.service_name %></h4>
                          </div>
                          <div class="modal-body">
                            <div class="row">
                              <div class="col-md-2">
                              </div>
                              <div class="col-md-8 ">
                                <p class="show">
                                  <br>
                                  <strong>Cost:</strong>
                                  $<%= service.cost %>
                                </p>

                                <p class="show">
                                  <strong>Time:</strong>
                                  <%= service.time %> minutes
                                </p>

                                <p class="show">
                                  <strong>Description:</strong>
                                  <%= service.description %>
                                </p>
                              </div>
                              <div class="col-md-2">
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        <div class="modal-footer">
                          <button type="button" class="service-btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                        </div>
                      </div>

                    </div>
                  </div>
                
          <% end %>
        </div>
  </div>